        },
        "subject": "LU-2622 obdclass: Add a preallocated percpu cl_env",
        "message": "LU-2622 obdclass: Add a preallocated percpu cl_env\n\nThis change adds support for a single preallocated cl_env per CPU\nwhich can be used in circumstances where reschedule is not possible.\nCurrently this interface is only used by the ll_releasepage function,\nto overcome a performance regression introduced by commit:\n\n    commit d5390bbde9b525b13ab91f5610abe1c4bb98eff9\n    LU-2622 obdclass: Remove the global cl_env list\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@intel.com>\nSigned-off-by: Prakash Surya <surya1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: I44d7b02f82c8e979731d9d4f849a3de262bfe91d\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
